---
description: Validate Navit shipped XML against navit.dtd before push
globs: **/*shipped.xml
alwaysApply: false
---

# *shipped.xml and DTD

CI runs:

```bash
xmllint --noout --dtdvalid navit/navit.dtd your_shipped.xml
```

Fix validation errors before pushing; DTD path is relative to the repository root.
